{"tid":1347791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:11.000Z","uid":264683,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf22074eec33d2daf7a333c5a8e640f95e6aea8c","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"元朗單野有幾重要唔再講<br />\n<br />\n理性少少，唔好再話元朗單野係轉移視線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343413</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想整合下兩黑嘅黑材料整張罪狀list<br />\n方便文宣組/ 各位手足傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑幫白衫惡行：<br />\n譴責內容：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">恐怖份子，波及無辜市民，進行無差別攻擊<br />\n為所欲為，無法無天</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.全部人手持木棍，鐵通<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BucMdL5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBucMdL5.png&h=40b8a31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsCHwB6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsCHwB6.png&h=2a65ea61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.多名普通街坊，包括長者，孕婦遭追打受襲，導致36人送院，1人危殆<br />\n3.多名記者被毆打，嚴重者頭破血流<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/660618832/posts/10157546397058833?s=1253604847&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F660618832%2Fposts%2F10157546397058833%3Fs%3D1253604847%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=49a69572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/660618832/posts/10157546397058833?s=1253604847&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGyb9jJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGyb9jJ.png&h=7f957780&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gx5NHEJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgx5NHEJ.png&h=88459a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.衝入西鐵站大堂，yoho出口，月台毆小市民，並歡呼拍掌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74ECkrf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74ECkrf.png&h=2744d7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/js7kicW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjs7kicW.png&h=754c5fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMVqujC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMVqujC.png&h=675c74b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警惡行<br />\n<br />\n譴責內容：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑黑相衛，選擇性執法，縱容暴力<br />\n維護治安不力，罔顧市民安危，市民求助無門</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.內部落Order，不制止白衫暴徒，有full gear警員standby，但不執<br />\n2.元朗警署落閘，999報案熱線被cut/ 打唔通<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0qU68s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0qU68s.png&h=f2fc5795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.西鐵站外舉紅旗，以掩護白衫暴徒離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcOb9mZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcOb9mZ.png&h=175ed253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.白衫sir被市民問及如何返屋企，態度惡劣<br />\n6.阻止記者進村內採訪- 記者聽到警方的傳呼機傳來「不要讓記者進來」。警察解釋是因為不清楚村內狀況。<br />\n7.警察反查普通市民身分證，搜市民身<br />\n<br />\n再睇下元朗指揮官游乃強up乜？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4VmM7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4VmM7m.png&h=4442bf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下班賣港賊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3frdDeN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3frdDeN.png&h=c44c9115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火力全開，<br />\n仲要追埋中上環嗰36槍<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全面追究黑黑暴力<br />\n全面譴責政府無能應急<br />\n全面討伐賣港議員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jJjyRg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jJjyRg.png&h=ab62f091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後歡迎各位巴絲繼續提供彈藥</span>"},{"pid":"7e4f98a6724ac5b24ba3b7a80ae4196fd6f71628","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4612e70c32f01c99fa3832abf76bf215ff8446ff","tid":1347791,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5b5ee437ea4736127961460f48fa44e956f21c","tid":1347791,"uid":269973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<br />\ndllm"},{"pid":"aeab9ea1902e0f8c7ca06875e3c843f551258558","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7296d9303d4b2311fa4aacbc5791141e54718d5","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推到政府壽終正寢</span></span>"},{"pid":"8be0f6d72f16d9910e3850efc005c9c9a1b61d34","tid":1347791,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1c0ed025c7abc92d91e983f0c958090562a6649c","tid":1347791,"uid":36742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！<br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b601adc1fbba95f52150926d197ab184c738ce2e","tid":1347791,"uid":193436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d501f8a18ea8d7d3b8ab42ac517235ea9f8d21d8","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a473dfa67049c9774237c976e43f8de88aa22c98","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b601adc1fbba95f52150926d197ab184c738ce2e","tid":1347791,"uid":193436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b008acec1b58be6d92854866ed49e79819c658","tid":1347791,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"bbb475cbd3bd9fc491fb8442bc8d5398bd136966","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"無差別攻擊<br />\n黑黑相衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a907612d7269e78d6e997e5509708fe3e6fb61d","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a31eb98e9291221fc254dcf30ce54bba80ce6a","tid":1347791,"uid":264683,"like":0,"disli